channel.title: Help playing on ANY server in Moparscape
channel.description:
Hello everyone... I just heard of Moparscape last Saturday and have been captivated by what can be done here. I quit playing runescape in 2003, but now that I hear the game can be edited and personally changed I want to play on some Moparscape servers. The problem:
1. ANY server I try to log on to says 'Unable to connect, server must be down, please try another server'.
2. I've checked my java on several occasions to see if I have the most updated version and it turns out I do..
3. The path to my Java IS set and I have confirmed this by going to the Jagex's www.runescape.com site and playing on their servers which works perfectly fine. I just can't play on any of the Mopar servers... I really want to play on the servers posted in this RS2 section so can anyone here please help me out?
